song.title: Blue Street
song.info:
Blue Street el blanco [fulcrum] a hair over 3 minutes (like 3:05)
Greetz to fulcrum members, especially Coplan! Yannick for making FT2, old skool #trax-ers and the rest.
This song has quite a few firsts for me. It's my first tune since joining [fulcrum], my first Mad Tracker 2 tune, and the first new song I've written in like...5 years.
It's a bit slow, but so am I now that I'm getting older. Enjoy.
